Package: mrf2d
Type: Package
Title: Markov Random Field Models for Image Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Freguglia
Maintainer: Victor Freguglia <victorfreguglia@gmail.com>
Description: Estimation and sampling of Markov Random Fields
    and Hidden Markov Random Fields defined on 2-dimensional lattices (images).
